{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-03117/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-03117"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:31:17"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["eye-level"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["two shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A man puts a coat on a woman."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03117/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-03117","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03117/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-03117"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03117/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03117/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03117/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03117/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03117/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03117/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03117/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03117/canvas/1/4889db93-373a-4929-be0a-30348c21e83a","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T13:50:53.503Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Reynolds continues to dress Alma as he helps her with her coat. He views her as something to shape and craft.</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03117/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:759.6116504854368,195.14563106796115,596.5048543689321,492.4271844660194"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03117/canvas/1/b2dae97e-4046-4842-a421-8c50695d0c57","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T13:51:08.418Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Alma’s voiceover narration suggests a different reading of this scene. She is in control of the story, as she’s the one telling it, and, moreover, she acknowledges that Reynolds’s clothing has given her a different experience with her body and self-perception. While some of their exchanges would suggest that Reynolds is the one in power, continually shaping Alma’s appearance, the words that underlie these moments reveal that theirs is a relationship built on a carefully calibrated exchange of power.</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03117/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:361.94174757281553,237.08737864077668,306.0194174757281,316.8932038834952"}}}]}]}]}